def {name}(key: int, seed: int) -> int:
    h = (key & 0xFFFFFFFF) * ((seed & 0xFFFFFFFF) | 1)
    h &= 0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF
    h ^= h >> 33
    h *= 0xff51afd7ed558ccd
    h &= 0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF
    h ^= h >> 33
    return h & 0xFFFFFFFF

    h = (key & 0xFFFFFFFF) * ((seed & 0xFFFFFFFF) | 1)
    h &= 0xFFFFFFFF
    h = (h ^ 61) ^ (h >> 16)
    h = (h * 9) & 0xFFFFFFFF
    h = h ^ (h >> 4)
    h = (h * 0x27d4eb2d) & 0xFFFFFFFF
    h = h ^ (h >> 15)
    h ^= ((1 + h) << 13) & 0xFFFFFFFF
    h &= 0xFFFFFFFF
    h ^= h >> 17
    h ^= (h << 5) & 0xFFFFFFFF
    return h & 0xFFFFFFFF
